id: pm-1p2u
title: "SDK invoke helpers for importers & exporters: runRegisteredImporterForTest + runRegisteredExporterForTest"
description: "Complete the SDK package-author 'invoke' verb by adding name-based invoke helpers for the last two executable registration surfaces without one: importers and exporters. registerImporter/registerExporter wrap their handlers into command paths ('<name> import' / '<name> export'), so today they are invokable only via runRegisteredCommandForTest with a hand-derived command path. The new runRegisteredImporterForTest(activation, { importer }) / runRegisteredExporterForTest(activation, { exporter }) resolve by registration name (validating via assertRegisteredImporter/Exporter), derive the command path internally, and return the same CommandHandlerResult. Now every executable register* surface has both an assertRegistered* and a runRegistered*ForTest counterpart."
type: Feature
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: "area:extensions","area:packages","area:sdk",extension-testing
created_at: "2026-06-21T19:14:23.653Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-21T19:58:41.576Z"
author: claude-code-agent
parent: pm-ugqx
resolution: "Shipped in PR #331 (squash 468ddb0e). Added runRegisteredImporterForTest + runRegisteredExporterForTest to src/sdk/testing.ts, completing the package-author invoke verb for every executable registration surface. Name-based resolution, internal command-path derivation, registration validation, verbatim CommandHandlerResult. Dogfooded end-to-end; 100% coverage; SDK.md + EXTENSIONS.md updated; Gemini doc-clarity finding addressed; all CI green."
